Step-1 connection

ENC28j60      -       pi zero w
vcc       -          pin 17
gnd       -          pin 20
cs        -          pin 24
si        -          pin 19
sck       -          pin 23
so        -          pin 21
INT       -          pin 22

Step-2
Scanner   -         PI zero
VCC       -         Pin 2
GND       -         Pin 6
TX        -         Pin 8
RX        -         Pin 10

Step-3
Relay     -         PI zero
vcc       -         pin 4
gnd       -         pin 9
IN        -         pin 11

Step-4 raspberrypi.local ko ping krenge bina ethernet cable lgaye wifi ke through
Step-5 vnc ke through raspberry pi ke desktop me enter krenge aur code ko run krenge
Step-6 is wale file me jayenge aur sara chiz ko likh denge isse ki sara uart pin enable ho jayega
go to /boot/firmware/config.txt
enable_uart=1
dtoverlay=uart0
dtoverlay=uart1
dtoverlay=uart2
dtoverlay=uart3
dtoverlay=uart4
dtoverlay=uart5



Step-5 sudo nano /boot/config.txt isme jayenge aur 
dtparam=spi=on
dtoverlay=enc28j60
aisa likh denge aur iske bad sudo reboot krenge
